column2: SELECT TOP #  s.ra, s.dec, g.d4#_sub, gSL.h_delta_flux FROM ..galSpecIndx as g  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.SpecobjID = g.SpecobjID JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.SpecobjID = g.SpecobjID JOIN SpecObj AS s  ON g.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID JOIN galSpecLine as gSL  ON gSL.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID
